      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>hot dog sausage[s] </strong>and cook for 10-12 min, turning frequently until browned all over and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
